The sys.cfg should be something like:

{
	"MQTT_SERVER"	:	"xxx",
	"MQTT_TOPIC"	:	"xxx",
	"MQTT_USER"	:	"xxx",
	"MQTT_PASSWD"	:	"xxx"
}

The command to create the RRD database:
rrdtool create miner_state.rrd --step 10s	\
	DS:sensors:GAUGE:20:0:10		\
	DS:miners:GAUGE:20:0:10			\
